The '''C-3 protocol droid''' was a household [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] that was manufactured on the factory [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Telti/Legends|Telti]] by [[Cybot Galactica/Legends|Cybot Galactica]]. It was programmed with many different functions. It was the predecessor of the [[C-4 protocol droid]] and the successor of the [[C-2 protocol droid]].

